-- KKR-Led Group Said to Agree to Purchase Del Monte Foods for $19 a Share
-- B y   M a t t h e w   B o y l e
-- 2010-11-25T17:50:28Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-11-25/kkr-led-group-said-to-agree-to-purchase-del-monte-foods-for-19-a-share.html
A group led by KKR & Co. agreed to
buy Del Monte Foods Co. for about $19 a share, according to a
person with direct knowledge of the transaction.  An announcement may be made as soon as today, said the
person, who declined to be identified because the talks are
private. The New York Times reported the deal earlier today.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Matthew Boyle in New York at 
